Revision history for Perl extension Mojolicious::Plugin::DataTables.

2.00  2021-03-20
    - Added support for SQL::Abstract
    - DEPRECATED "db" option (use "sql" instead)
    - Improved documentations

1.03  2020-03-30
    - Improved "where" param with SQL bind values

1.02  2020-03-29
    - Added "where" param
    - Changed boolean condition for columns search (OR -> AND)

1.01  2020-03-29
    - Added support for DataTables "regex" option using REGEXP (MySQL and SQLite)
      or "~" SQL operators (PostgreSQL)
    - Changed minumum required Perl version (>= 5.10)
    - Added "examples" directory
    - Fixed documentation typo

1.00  2020-03-25
    - First release of Mojolicious::Plugin::DataTables

